                  <br> Don't forget to be polite with others.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-inverted">
            <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid"
                src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/11/08/05/10/students-1807505_1280.jpg" alt=""></div>
            <div class="timeline-panel">
              <div class="timeline-heading">
                <h4>Choose your buddy</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-body">
                <p class="text-muted">Choose an assistant that you like, or receive an incoming requests from buddies
