              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="timeline-image"><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid"
                src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/08/05/01/12/phone-875488_1280.jpg" alt=""></div>
            <div class="timeline-panel">
              <div class="timeline-heading">
                <h4>Talk with buddy</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-body">
                <p class="text-muted">Discuss all request details, clarify request cost with your buddy and decide would
                  you agree or not.
                  Make sure you both understand conditions and final price.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-inverted">
            <div class="timeline-image bg-primary">
              <h4>
                Enjoy!
              </h4>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="showcase py-0">
      <div class="container-fluid p-0">
        <div class="row no-gutters">

          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 text-white showcase-img"
            style="background-image: url('https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/11/16/03/37/globe-trotter-1828079_1280.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
            <h2>What if I am traveller?</h2>
            <p class="lead mb-0">You need to go through a simple registration and choose your assistant. Assistants are
              always in the city of your stay. All assistants speak your language and the language of the country where
              you arrived.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters">
          <div class="col-lg-6 text-white showcase-img" style="background-position-y: center; background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542380536-3eb944a532d8?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=934&q=80');"></div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 my-auto showcase-text">
            <h2>Can I become buddy?</h2>
            <p class="lead mb-0">Of course yes! If you think that your city is popular for tourists and you have
              something to show and tell, then feel free to register in our service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="landing-subscribe" class="bg-light">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
          <h2>Get started today</h2>
          <h4 class="text-muted">Subsctibe to receive notification on launch!</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto js-subsctiption-wrapper">
            <form method="POST" action="#" class="js-subscription-form subscription-form mt-5">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="name@company.com" class="form-control">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  {{> templates/footer}}
  <script>
    /**
    * Parallax scroll effect
    * Created by Sallar Kaboli <sallar.kaboli@gmail.com>
    */
    var $content = document.querySelector('.welcome .welcome-content')
      , $blur = document.querySelector('.welcome .welcome-overlay')
      , wHeight = window.innerHeight;

    window.addEventListener('resize', function () {
      wHeight = window.innerHeight;
    });

    /**
     * requestAnimationFrame Shim 
     */
    window.requestAnimFrame = (function () {
      return window.requestAnimationFrame ||
        window.webkitRequestAnimationFrame ||
        window.mozRequestAnimationFrame ||
        function (callback) {
          window.setTimeout(callback, 1000 / 60);
        };
    })();

    /**
     * Scroller
     */
    function Scroller() {
      this.latestKnownScrollY = 0;
      this.ticking = false;
    }

    Scroller.prototype = {
      /**
       * Initialize
       */
      init: function () {
        window.addEventListener('scroll', this.onScroll.bind(this), false);
      },

      /**
       * Capture Scroll
       */
      onScroll: function () {
        this.latestKnownScrollY = window.scrollY;
        this.requestTick();
      },

      /**
       * Request a Tick
       */
      requestTick: function () {
        if (!this.ticking) {
          window.requestAnimFrame(this.update.bind(this));
        }
        this.ticking = true;
      },

      /**
       * Update.
       */
      update: function () {
        var currentScrollY = this.latestKnownScrollY;
        this.ticking = false;

        /**
         * Do The Dirty Work Here
         */
        var slowScroll = currentScrollY / 4,
          blurScroll = currentScrollY * 2;

        $content.style.transform = 'translateY(-' + slowScroll + 'px)';

        $blur.style.opacity = blurScroll / wHeight;
      }
    };

    /**
     * Attach!
     */
    var scroller = new Scroller();
    scroller.init();
  </script>
</body>

</html>